snippet.title: SHARK SEASON | Can They Reach Shore Before Time Runs Out? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
Three kayakers are stranded near a remote island.
Getting home means facing the danger waiting in the water.

While kayaking near a remote island, three friends find themselves stranded with no immediate way back to the mainland. As they wait for help, rising tides and open water force them to make a dangerous decision. With time running out, their only path to safety leads straight through waters they may not survive.

Director: Jared Cohn
Cast: Michael Madsen, Paige McGarvin, Juliana DeStefano, Jack Pearson.
